All Implemented Interfaces:
IUIPropertySupport, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.SwingConstants
public class JYPreferencesPanel
extends JYTabbedPane

The PreferencesPanel is optimized for preference settings. It is based on a JYTabbedPane and provides a different style. Note: The default name is "JYPreferencesPanel" - modifying name results in a different style.

Version:
1.01, 09.11.2009
See Also:
JYTabbedPane, Serialized Form
